				</div>

				<p>
					Prototipo de shooter tactico hardcore.
				</p>

				<div class="tech">
					<span>C#</span>
					<span>Unity</span>
					<span>Animacion 3D</span>
					<span>Scripting</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- ================= EFI ================= -->
