				</div>

				<p>
					Plataforma educativa de nueva generacion, orientada a comunicacion, educacion y administracion.
				</p>

				<div class="tech">
					<span>Flutter</span>
					<span>Dart</span>
					<span>Django</span>
					<span>Arquitectura Modular</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- ================= PLANE VIEWER ================= -->
